name: Darling, I'm transforming into a Pepe
description:
Every destiny, no matter how long and intricate, actually consists of a single moment: the moment when the man knows forever what kind of Pepe he will become.

.

In the year 2029, numerous scientific studies were conducted with evidence that humans were turning into amphibians. Precisely in toads.

Studies with similar applications were carried out for the first time in 2012. But they were buried in oblivion. Apparently, they were detrimental to giant laboratories in the fertilizer and genetically modified seed industry.
